title: A Breakdown Can Be a Good Thing
itunes:title: A Breakdown Can Be a Good Thing
description:
Sometimes a breakdown and confusion can show you that you are really close to a breakthrough. In this episode, I will teach you how to use a breakdown to grow! 

 

Do you want to learn how to make $100k+ a year as a coach or consultant? If so, join my FREE 4-day workshop called The 6 Figure Coaching System on August 24-27th here: https://www.6figurecoachingsystem.com/
